Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.11,0:26:28.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏に流れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.16,0:26:32.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}制服の群れに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.51,0:26:37.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}逆らうよに　自転車の
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:42.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}ペダル　思いきり踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.42,0:26:46.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放課後のグランドの脇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.85,0:26:50.27,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}金網をくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.33,0:26:55.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年　見つけた　ひまわりは
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.79,0:27:00.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年より　誇らしげに
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.23,0:27:03.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}空を見上げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:09.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}折れないように　枯れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:12.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}涙に出来たなら
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.41,0:27:19.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明日は何かが変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.39,0:27:26.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}雨降る日は　雨に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.80,0:27:31.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}あの　ひまわりみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.40,0:27:35.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}まっすぐ　背を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.70,0:27:42.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}今日は揺れていたって、いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.11,0:26:28.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏下  逆行在流动的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.16,0:26:32.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}身着制服的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.51,0:26:37.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}尽情地  蹬踩着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:42.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}自行车的脚踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.42,0:26:46.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放学后  操场边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.85,0:26:50.27,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}钻过铁丝网
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.33,0:26:55.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年发现的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.79,0:27:00.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}比以往还要骄傲地
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.23,0:27:03.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:09.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}不屈不挠  不会枯萎地
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:12.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}若是放声哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.41,0:27:19.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明天又会变得怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.39,0:27:26.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}下雨的日子  在雨中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.80,0:27:31.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}就像那朵向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.40,0:27:35.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}挺直了腰杆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.70,0:27:42.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}哪怕今日有所动摇  也无所谓
