Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}佐藤先生来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}请你速到办公室来
