Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}…穿时髦而费事的系带鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旭日祭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做企划的话就得必须快点申请啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还有新闻部的企划要做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻部也要做企划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是地下社团吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是地下社团也做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻部要做什么企划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…还没有决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗  你最近很少陪我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你加入新闻部以后就很少一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日也经常不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好伤心！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:52.30,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}闲杂人等禁止入内\N新闻部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:52.30,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}园\N原\N电\N波\N新\N闻\N部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须藤特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了保守机密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来的时候也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长今天好象跷了一整天的课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的是园原基地  而那个是幽灵战斗机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,441)\fs21}Foo Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是咱们园原电波新闻部的旭日祭企划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于UFO现象的调查报告与展示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主题就是「园原基地的幽灵战斗机」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种大事为什么是由你自己一个人擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是说\N我和浅羽怎么想都无关紧要是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有在学园祭上想做的事情吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么特殊想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是大家都想做的企划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没有自己的想法吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽特派员的意思是「交由别人来思考企划」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算是一种意见不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自决定再怎么说也太霸道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  须藤特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做其他企划的话也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也可以一起做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  晶穗你想做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在明天前会仔细考虑好的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头  剪刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火腿三明治  猪排三明治  鸡蛋三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金枪鱼三明治  水果三明治外加橙汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  太大意了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  炒面味的杯面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加辣味美乃滋的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卖部可不卖这东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录像带店对面的便利店应该有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者①超市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳赢了部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  要稍微出去走一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头有点痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  可是不完成这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽你明天也要想出点什么来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事也要告诉伊里野一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了  不用理她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛要护着她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穂你刚刚不是还在对着部长坚持说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团内的企划应该经全体讨论之后再决定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  那为什么还要把\N伊里野一个人排除在外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我讨厌她！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的每个人也都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人想和她做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只要实际跟她聊过天你就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野她并不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么理由  让我非得主动跟她友好不可啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是觉得不需要什么朋友吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.71,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有七天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好考虑过吗？  企划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗想到什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发行日刊「园原电波新闻部旭日祭特别号」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野今天来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没看到人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然还没看到人  那你怎么知道她来了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}二年四班的伊里野加奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}铃木先生来电
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}请你速到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.82,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(209,430)}发布命令。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.82,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(350,450)}今天0750，防卫体制(DEFCON)由Lv5上升到Lv4。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.82,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(396,470)}非常召集除对应机以外的所有配备机、驾驶员、支援人员。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}伊里野加奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}请你速到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}真是的  大清早的又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然之前就觉得很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木啊佐藤啊  这都是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那广播到底算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（课文出自夏目漱石的《こころ》下  先生と遺書  34）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}我问K是不是和小姐一块儿出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}K说不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}是在真砂町偶然碰上  搭伴回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}这次北军势力对38度\N海域封锁的目的现在仍不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}日前举行的记者招待会上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要问为什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}自卫军与美军正在加紧对该海域封锁解除的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在是上课时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是早退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近经常在请假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是早退了  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了一小时的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你是怎么知道我在这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道学园祭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校…庆？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  学园祭你想做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是食物摊子还是咖啡店都行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是部长的企划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还没有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么…做出来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有UFO狂拍摄到的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从知名的到奇奇怪怪的都有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部收集起来的话还是相当多的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此作为参考…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  这是园原基地的模型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的话感觉还是相当不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然用展示来作为企划\N有点太不起眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了这个季节了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.29,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}知了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.32,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有7天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.02,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有6天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你觉得我们班上谁的身材最好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正黑体_GBK}辻{\r}  或者杉山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得是杉山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有伊里野也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  感觉整体线条相当匀称哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经验者来说下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  浅羽人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回学校了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:12:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙最近很少出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道哪里有梯子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…想来送些吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃泡面就要在房顶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我为数不多的原则之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想见你一面  跟你好好道声谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野下次什么时候再来学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.33,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有4天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:13:59.84,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有3天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:00.34,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有2天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:00.94,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有1天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.01,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距「旭日祭」还有1天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.72,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「旭日祭」第{\1c&2725b9}1{\r}天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这不是西久保吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是浅羽的爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  直之一直以来承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  西久保
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  下午兵分两路去取材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直之是不是有女朋友了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才和西久保都说了些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之间的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻…新闻部的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  你是直之还是夕子的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是新闻部的…须藤…晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和浅羽直之同班…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…听说浅羽的父母来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得必须打个招呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  令人烦恼的年纪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绘  你真的是椎名老师的学妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绘真不像是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫先坂老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体温正常！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.77,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}别找我  外出中(工事)  先坂老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝醉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  喝醉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧地问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有和这很像的人\N来过府上的理发店呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  好像帮不上你什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  请问两位明天要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看夕子演出的戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的话一定得去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.49,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「旭日祭」第{\1c&2725b9}1{\r}天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.86,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「旭日祭」第{\1c&FFA500\N}2{\r}天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过号外了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是浅羽做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误排三处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来我也有事情要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都说了「对不起」了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你这是什么态度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里了啊  昨晚！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭是咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以晚上直接回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完咖喱后洗完澡就睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你接下来打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么预定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你这个没有女朋友的悲惨青少年\N我就委屈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为赔礼  陪你去篝火晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是觉得你好象不太喜欢土风舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没练习过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要练习后才能跳土风舞多丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻也是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人是练习过后才做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你醉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你已经练习过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说清楚啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有还是没有！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位？…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  自己能走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}最新新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}北军情势越趋紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}最近对于38度周边海域的飞机船只
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}自卫军与美军发出了全面撤离的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}重复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}位于38度周边海域的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:51.79,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}选美会场  园原小姐  这边←  决定！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的园原小姐是椎名真由美小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:55.10,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}第23届  园原中选美  冠军揭晓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}啊  二年四班的浅羽直之同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}二年四班的浅羽直之同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}伊里野加奈同学来电
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}请你速到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在电话里确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请迅速归队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lv3？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Lv1待机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时隔两年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正  总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里打电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这是禁止使用的线路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讲太久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你静静听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆上自卫军的旧园原演习场知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有个叫做「六番山」的山丘  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  18点45分在那里等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要自己一个人来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不能再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽同学是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  这次我就不追究了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私人原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事…想要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丫头在你面前总是表现得一本正经的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可一回到基地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就老是念着浅羽说了这个  浅羽说了那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间白天回来后也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴里一直念叨着要和浅羽一起参加学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  我就顺嘴问了一句
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「篝火晚会也和浅羽一起吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野现在已经知道了篝火晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听了土风舞的事之后  那丫头就兴奋得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的脑海中…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起在篝火晚会上跳土风舞这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经成了既定事项了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也尽了最大努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能让伊里野参加学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从目前情况来看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能说是…希望渺茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…如果能赶上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你陪伊里野跳土风舞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.70,0:24:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.36,0:24:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩上的重担现在轻点了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.15,0:25:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  停了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.88,0:26:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋


